<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Katabatic</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f3f1fa;
    --surface: #ffffff;
    --accent: #7a6db5;
    --text: #2c2841;
    --accent-10: rgba(122, 109, 181, 0.10);
    --accent-15: rgba(122, 109, 181, 0.15);
    --accent-25: rgba(122, 109, 181, 0.25);
    --accent-40: rgba(122, 109, 181, 0.40);
    --accent-06: rgba(122, 109, 181, 0.06);
    --text-60: rgba(44, 40, 65, 0.60);
    --text-35: rgba(44, 40, 65, 0.35);
    --text-20: rgba(44, 40, 65, 0.20);
    --text-08: rgba(44, 40, 65, 0.08);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 400;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* ─── WORDMARK LOGO ─── */
  .wordmark-hero {
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .wordmark {
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent-10);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2.8rem;
    margin-top: 2.4rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.05rem;
  }

  .meta-item .label {
    font-size: 0.54rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-35);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .meta-item .value {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ─── DIVIDER ─── */
  .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--text-08); margin: 0; }

  /* ─── SECTIONS ─── */
  section { padding: 3rem 0; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.54rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }

  .section-desc {
    color: var(--text-60);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─── PROBLEM CARDS ─── */
  .thesis-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .thesis-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .thesis-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-25);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .thesis-card .stat {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .thesis-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .thesis-card p {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─── SIGNAL CARDS ─── */
  .signals-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .signal-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.3rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .signal-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-25);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .signal-icon-wrap {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-10);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .signal-icon-wrap svg {
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.8;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .signal-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .signal-card p {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .signal-card .source {
    font-size: 0.56rem;
    color: var(--text-35);
    margin-top: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ─── ARCHITECTURE ─── */
  .arch-pipeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .arch-layer {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem;
  }

  .arch-layer .layer-label {
    font-size: 0.52rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-35);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .layer-num {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    width: 17px; height: 17px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .arch-layer h3 {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .arch-layer p {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .arch-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    margin-top: 0.7rem;
  }

  .arch-tag {
    background: var(--accent-06);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-15);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ─── TIMELINE ─── */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 4.5px;
    top: 6px;
    bottom: 6px;
    width: 1.5px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--accent-25), var(--text-08));
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .tl-block {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }

  .tl-block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -1.72rem;
    top: 5px;
    width: 11px; height: 11px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .tl-block:nth-child(2) .tl-dot { border-color: var(--accent-40); }
  .tl-block:nth-child(3) .tl-dot { border-color: var(--accent-40); }
  .tl-block:nth-child(4) .tl-dot { border-color: var(--accent-25); }
  .tl-block:nth-child(5) .tl-dot { border-color: var(--text-20); }

  .tl-time {
    font-size: 0.56rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .tl-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .tl-block p {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .tl-tasks {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tl-chip {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    padding: 0.16rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ─── TEAM ─── */
  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.3rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .team-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-25); }

  .team-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.6rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--accent-10);
  }

  .team-icon svg {
    width: 18px; height: 18px;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.8;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .team-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .team-card .role-desc {
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─── DEMO BOX ─── */
  .demo-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accent-25);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .demo-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .demo-header-icon {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-10);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .demo-header-icon svg {
    width: 15px; height: 15px;
    stroke: var(--accent);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.8;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .demo-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .demo-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .demo-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-size: 0.56rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    background: var(--accent);
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .demo-step p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .demo-step p strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .demo-step p em {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ─── IMPACT ─── */
  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .impact-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.6rem 1.2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .impact-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-25); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .impact-num {
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .impact-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .impact-card p {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─── PITCH ─── */
  .pitch-flow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pitch-step {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1rem 0.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pitch-step::after {
    content: '›';
    position: absolute;
    right: -0.4rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: var(--accent-40);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .pitch-step:last-child::after { display: none; }

  .pitch-step .time {
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .pitch-step h4 {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .pitch-step p {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text-60);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-line {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--text-08);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-wordmark {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: lowercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  footer p {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--text-35);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .thesis-grid, .signals-grid, .impact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .team-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .pitch-flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pitch-step::after { display: none; }
    .hero-meta { gap: 1.5rem; }
    .container { padding: 0 1.2rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <!-- ════ HERO ════ -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge">Cornell AI Hackathon 2026 · Programmable Capital</div>
    <div class="wordmark-hero">katabatic</div>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">Climate-Aware Stablecoin<br>Risk Intelligence</div>
    <p class="hero-sub">The first stablecoin risk scoring system that models real-world exposure: weather, macro, and regulatory, not just on-chain metrics.</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="label">Track</span>
        <span class="value">Programmable Capital</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="label">Team</span>
        <span class="value">4 to 5 Engineers</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="label">Build Window</span>
        <span class="value">36 Hours</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="label">Core Skill</span>
        <span class="value">ML / Data Science</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- ════ PROBLEM ════ -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-label">01 The Problem</div>
    <div class="section-title">Stablecoin risk is real. Current tools are blind.</div>
    <p class="section-desc">$150B+ sits in stablecoins. Existing risk tools only look at on-chain data. Nobody's modeling the real-world exposure that actually causes depegs.</p>
    <div class="thesis-grid">
      <div class="thesis-card">
        <div class="stat">$150B+</div>
        <h3>Stablecoin Market Cap</h3>
        <p>Massive capital in assets whose risk profiles are poorly understood by holders and protocols alike.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="thesis-card">
        <div class="stat">UST → $0</div>
        <h3>Precedent: Terra Collapse</h3>
        <p>$60B wiped out. On-chain metrics looked healthy until they didn't. Existing tools missed it entirely.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="thesis-card">
        <div class="stat">70%</div>
        <h3>Backed by Real-World Assets</h3>
        <p>Treasuries, commodities, and bonds exposed to macro forces like interest rates, weather, and geopolitics. All invisible on-chain.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="thesis-card">
        <div class="stat">0</div>
        <h3>Tools Modeling This</h3>
        <p>No one scores stablecoins against climate exposure, macro stress, or real-world collateral risk. We're the first.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- ════ RISK SIGNALS ════ -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-label">02 Risk Signal Architecture</div>
    <div class="section-title">Six dimensions. One composite score.</div>
    <p class="section-desc">We go beyond on-chain by ingesting weather, macro, and regulatory data to build a multi-dimensional risk profile per stablecoin.</p>
    <div class="signals-grid">
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="signal-icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 2v4m0 12v4m-10-10h4m12 0h4m-2.64-7.36l-2.83 2.83m-8.49 8.49l-2.83 2.83m0-14.14l2.83 2.83m8.49 8.49l2.83 2.83"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Peg Stability</h4>
        <p>Historical deviation from $1.00, volatility clustering, recovery speed after shocks, max drawdown events.</p>
        <div class="source">CoinGecko · DeFiLlama</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="signal-icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="10" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 10V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Reserve Health</h4>
        <p>Audit frequency, collateral composition, counterparty concentration, asset-liability duration mismatch.</p>
        <div class="source">Issuer reports · SEC filings</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="signal-icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 14.9A7 7 0 1 1 15.7 8h1.8a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 .5 8.97"/><path d="M8 19h.01M12 17h.01M8 13h.01M16 15h.01M12 21h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Climate Exposure</h4>
        <p>Weather events affecting commodity collateral, insurance-linked reserves, energy market stress, regional banking.</p>
        <div class="source">NOAA · OpenMeteo · NHC</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="signal-icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2zm0 0a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-9c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h2"/><path d="M18 14h-8m8-4h-8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Sentiment & News</h4>
        <p>LLM-scored sentiment on regulatory actions, team changes, exploit reports, and market commentary.</p>
        <div class="source">News APIs · LLM analysis</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="signal-icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>On-Chain Concentration</h4>
        <p>Whale wallet concentration, smart contract age, audit status, recent large transfers, DEX liquidity depth.</p>
        <div class="source">Etherscan · Dune Analytics</div>
      </div>
      <div class="signal-card">
        <div class="signal-icon-wrap">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Regulatory Exposure</h4>
        <p>Issuer jurisdiction risk, pending enforcement actions, licensing status, compliance framework maturity.</p>
        <div class="source">Public filings · LLM extraction</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- ════ ARCHITECTURE ════ -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-label">03 Technical Architecture</div>
    <div class="section-title">From raw signals to explainable risk.</div>
    <p class="section-desc">A four-layer pipeline: ingest multi-source data, engineer features, score with ML, and explain in plain English.</p>
    <div class="arch-pipeline">
      <div class="arch-layer">
        <div class="layer-label"><span class="layer-num">1</span> Data Ingestion</div>
        <h3>Multi-Source Real-Time Feeds</h3>
